BodLatMisC66.First Lines:
By god of loue set I nothyngnor by venus with her vayn glorie I
                    wold not aplyffor I thogh playnly all my h[ ]…
BodLatMisC66.Last Lines:
…bot and sho do I de this dieand of my dethe sho is the
                    wite
